OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FFifteen miles south of York, a
OL,7,     Fprolific car thief crashes and
OL,8,     Frolls a stolen car at over 100mph.
OL,9,     FIn Harrogate, the hunt for a
OL,10,     Fdisqualified driver leads to a
OL,11,     Fhigh-speed pursuit.
OL,12,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FAfter a high speed pursuit,
OL,14,     Finterceptor Liam Sewell hunts down
OL,15,     Fa wanted teenager. Jacko plays a
OL,16,     Fgame of cat-and-mouse with a
OL,17,     Fyouth.
OL,18,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,19,     FPresenters Rick Edwards and Ortis
OL,20,     FDelay are out with the police
OL,21,     Finterceptors as they tackle the
OL,22,     Fdifficult night shift.
