OL,5,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FIn this special episode, the
OL,7,     Finterceptor's take on the young
OL,8,     Fand reckless who cause carnage on
OL,9,     Four roads and put themselves and
OL,10,     Fothers in danger.
OL,11,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up
OL,12,     FFollowing the work of enforcement
OL,13,     Fagents as they execute High Court
OL,14,     FWrits. In Worthing, agents visit a
OL,15,     Fswimming pool installation
OL,16,     Fbusiness to recover money for a
OL,17,     Fcustomer.
OL,18,G1800 Home and Away
OL,19,     FHarper avoids a hard truth. Alf
OL,20,     Fand Roo work to heal. Tane
OL,21,     Fsupports Mackenzie.
