OL,5,G2300 The Surgeon
OL,6,     FWe follow consultant brain surgeon
OL,7,     FOmar Pathmanaban as he tackles a
OL,8,     Frare tumour that could be fatal,
OL,9,     Fand also a complex and demanding
OL,10,     Fprocedure requiring surgery via
OL,11,     Fthe nose. (Ep3/4)
OL,12,G0000 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Adil Sheraz removes a giant
OL,14,     Flipoma from a patient's back,
OL,15,     Fwhile Dr Toby Nelson tackles 13
OL,16,     Flipomas on a single patient, and
OL,17,     Fthere's a nasty face cyst for Dr
OL,18,     FEmma McMullen.
