OL,5,G0100 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,6,     FBen from Lewisham Council's Rogue
OL,7,     FLandlord Unit has just 24 hours to
OL,8,     Frehouse a single mother and her
OL,9,     Fchild or they will end up on the
OL,10,     Fstreets.
OL,11,G0200 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,12,     FMargaret tries to get the #20,000
OL,13,     Fshe is owed from a letting agent,
OL,14,     FStavros and Emily try to get their
OL,15,     Fhouse back from squatters.
OL,16,G0250 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,17,     FThis episode sees a couple whose
OL,18,     Ftenant was using their property to
OL,19,     Fscam students out of deposits.
